      <title>缅甸昂山素季儿子担心被用作“人盾”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmars-suu-kyi-being-used-human-shield-son-fears-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸被拘留的前领导人和昂山素季被从监狱转移到软禁，她的儿子周四表示，该东南亚国家的执政军政府可能将其用作与抵抗战士冲突的人盾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmars-suu-kyi-being-used-human-shield-son-fears-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯和塔吉克斯坦士兵举行反恐演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/soldiers-russia-tajikistan-stage-counter-terrorist-drills-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯和塔吉克斯坦军队周四在这个中亚国家完成了为期几天的联合演习，演练应对武装分子或非法武装团体跨境入侵的场景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/soldiers-russia-tajikistan-stage-counter-terrorist-drills-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马尔代夫法院推翻前总统亚明的刑期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-court-overturns-ex-president-yameens-jail-term-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，马尔代夫高等法院推翻了前总统阿卜杜拉·亚明 11 年监禁，并要求下级法院重新启动针对他的刑事诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-court-overturns-ex-president-yameens-jail-term-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电预估台湾地震损失达9240万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-estimates-losses-924-mln-due-taiwan-earthquake-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾芯片制造商台积电表示，4 月 3 日发生的至少 25 年来最严重的地震给该公司第二季度带来了估计损失 30 亿新台币（合 9244 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-estimates-losses-924-mln-due-taiwan-earthquake-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:06:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将向英国和澳大利亚减少 80% 的许可以提振 AUKUS</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-reduce-licensing-by-80-uk-australia-boost-aukus-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商务部正在缩减对澳大利亚和英国的出口管制要求，以促进这三个国家 AUKUS 安全协议下的国防贸易，减少价值超过 75 亿美元的贸易许可负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-reduce-licensing-by-80-uk-australia-boost-aukus-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织告诉亚洲央行不要过于密切地关注美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-tells-asian-central-banks-not-follow-fed-too-closely-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织周四敦促亚洲央行关注国内通胀，避免将政策决定与美联储的预期举措过于紧密地联系在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-tells-asian-central-banks-not-follow-fed-too-closely-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，由于担心机密，俄罗斯收紧官员旅行规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-tightens-officials-travel-rules-due-fears-over-secrets-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[九名消息人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯正在加大一些官员出国旅行的难度，因为担心外国势力可能会在与西方关系60多年来最严重的危机期间试图获取国家机密。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-tightens-officials-travel-rules-due-fears-over-secrets-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东盟外长敦促缅甸停止边境暴力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-urge-cessation-myanmar-border-violence-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚各国外交部长周四敦促缅甸边境地区立即停止暴力，表达对平民福祉的担忧以及开展对话的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-urge-cessation-myanmar-border-violence-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与新西兰签署协议，共同关注南海问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周四同意深化防务合作，并对菲律宾和中国在南海发生海上冲突表示严重关切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:51:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和新西兰将关系提升为“全面伙伴关系”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-elevate-relations-comprehensive-partnership-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周四表示，菲律宾和新西兰将在 2026 年将关系提升为“全面伙伴关系”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-elevate-relations-comprehensive-partnership-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
